**Summary**


Knauf is looking for 1 figure to be placed in the Technical Department, who will be engaged in carrying out the following activities:

* Training on Drywall Systems, Knauf products, and their use;
* In\-depth study of static, seismic, thermal, acoustic and fire prevention issues as applied to Drywall Systems;
* Application of Knauf Dry Systems within design solutions;
* In\-depth knowledge and evaluation of systems required by the market;
* Acquisition of skills on competitor analysis;
* Product compliance training on technical documentation management and proper CE marking;
* Support in product test management and system certifications;
* Support in the technical development of digital platforms;
* Collaboration in the development of special projects.

